首要零件繪製如下
其餘零件如法炮製
&lt;iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/206266484" width="640" height="325" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
